    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a definitive example of mechanical purity. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies, mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. The vehicle has undergone a comprehensive mechanical refresh, including a proactive VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry remains tight, providing the telepathic turn-in these chassis are known for. Finished in a deep Carbon Black with a pristine Nappa leather interior, the aesthetic condition is commensurate with its mechanical excellence\u2014no oxidation, no panel gap variance, and a perfectly preserved underbody. A turn-key investment for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
